 DSL, in contrast, becomes a\nnon-abelian chiral spin liquid described by the $SU(2)_3$ topological order,\nwith Fibonacci-like anyons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Dec 2020 18:20:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-18"}
