volution models fail to predict some of the structures in the observed\npopulation of both the HeB and RGB stars. Further stellar model improvements\nare needed to reproduce the exact distributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Dec 2020 03:47:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-06"}
